{"tid":2207313,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國黑人喺上海嘉里中心偷嘢，店員發現後佢鬧店員廿分鍾","createTime":"2020-09-18T05:36:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-18T06:16:47.000Z","uid":313615,"like":22,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"e3bb730f950a3b53aa271f7b1c940ea3d8433eff","tid":2207313,"uid":313615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T05:36:58.000Z","msg":"9月13日，上海浦東嘉里城屈臣氏一名外籍男子通過掃描密碼購買咗2件商品，但佢手中嘅兩盒邦迪冇付款。驗貨時仲鬧店員，店內嘅顧客勸阻被鬧管閑事。<br />\n<br />\n一位美國黑人指攝像者話「下次唔好理閑事。攝像者答「你一直喺鬧人」<br />\n<br />\n黑人話「係，我鬧人，因為我係美國人，而你係中國人。」<br />\n<br />\n旁觀者話「呢度係一個講文明嘅國家。」<br />\n<br />\n黑人話「不，中國人食動物，中國人砍小孩，中國人乜都做。」<br />\n<br />\n旁觀者問「你點解留喺中國？」<br />\n<br />\n黑人話「點解要留喺中國？點解中國人仲喺美國？」<br />\n<br />\n屈臣氏工作人員回應「具體情況仲喺調查，我琴日冇上班，警方已經介入調查。」<br />\n<br />\n上海都有探頭，上海警察仲冇拉到呢個黑人，可能鬧得仲唔夠戳心？"},{"pid":"022d441b8589bb0701546960258cad3577fa7679","tid":2207313,"uid":201604,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T05:37:46.000Z","msg":"點解唔畀偷？當我地力架唔係人？<br />\nblack lives matter！"},{"pid":"68fe83c027f9dbd59590b8b1d68c832fb677da77","tid":2207313,"uid":313615,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T05:39:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TCDXznS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTCDXznS.jpg&h=34250697&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MfDTR9w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMfDTR9w.jpg&h=6f0facad&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7cd3a19f77f8f75a793479b2e31729d71edc7610","tid":2207313,"uid":301989,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T05:39:50.000Z","msg":"廣州blm<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3416abc0853abef2b07a11a50b948e6d32bf5ae1","tid":2207313,"uid":45255,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T05:41:53.000Z","msg":"學支那人耍無賴姐"},{"pid":"a4cc19fff487dc18a9516db51b5df8a31fbab89d","tid":2207313,"uid":83251,"like":1,"dislike":1,"scor